Jetstorm:
Melchana! I request to go and represent the Tripredacus! I am able to 
fly and go there!

Melchana:
Shut up! Why should you go more than anyone else here? You can't even 
transform!

Thrust:
Besides, I can fly too! But I would make a lousy diplomat...

Jetstorm:
That's my point! I can't transform, so I represent no danger for them! 
Had Daemos been online by now, I guess he would be a lot better than 
me on this, but he is not. As for strika, she has been asked on a 
mission by Gesper. So I request this assignment.

Melchana:
............................
Then go, and make the Tripredacus proud...

Jetstorm:
Thank you, trainer.

He flies off away from australia and to South America.
